<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 18:09:21 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>着眼中国：日本推出二战以来第一艘完整航母</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/eye-on-china-japan-launches-first-full-aircraft-carrier-since-wwii/articleshow/109202607.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109202607.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;日本将加贺号军舰改造为二战以来该国第一艘成熟的航空母舰，在其军事现代化努力中取得了一个值得注意的里程碑。加贺号此前被指定为直升机航母，现已进行了大幅改进，以适应 F-35 闪电 II 隐形战斗机的部署，这标志着日本防御能力在地区紧张局势升级的情况下进入了转型阶段。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 16:06:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/eye-on-china-japan-launches-first-full-aircraft-carrier-since-wwii/articleshow/109202607.cms</guid></item><item><title>“这似乎不对”：美国穆斯林在加沙战争中庆祝开斋节</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/it-doesnt-seem-right-muslim-americans-observe-muted-eid-amid-gaza-war/articleshow/109202471.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109202471.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 15:50:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/it-doesnt-seem-right-muslim-americans-observe-muted-eid-amid-gaza-war/articleshow/109202471.cms</guid></item><item><title>为什么美国立法者希望对中国公民实行严格的签证规定</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-lawmakers-for-strict-visa-rules-to-protect-us-military-secrets-from-chinese-espionage/articleshow/109201689.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109201689.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 15:42:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-lawmakers-for-strict-visa-rules-to-protect-us-military-secrets-from-chinese-espionage/articleshow/109201689.cms</guid></item><item><title>巨大的财富转移：中国如何改变全球黄金市场动态</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/a-great-wealth-transfer-how-china-is-changing-global-gold-market-dynamics/articleshow/109201685.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109201685.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 15:37:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/a-great-wealth-transfer-how-china-is-changing-global-gold-market-dynamics/articleshow/109201685.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦：卡拉奇人民在开斋节庆祝活动中继续面临严重缺水问题</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-people-in-karachi-continue-to-face-acute-water-shortages-amid-eid-ul-fitr-celebrations/articleshow/109201598.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109201598.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;卡拉奇在开斋节期间面临水资源短缺，影响多个地区。卡拉奇供水和污水处理公司负责管理供应，而居民则求助于替代水源。油轮黑手党利用节日期间的情况影响供水。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 15:20:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-people-in-karachi-continue-to-face-acute-water-shortages-amid-eid-ul-fitr-celebrations/articleshow/109201598.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦国际航空从沙特起飞的载有巴基斯坦总理谢赫巴兹·谢里夫的航班改道飞往拉合尔，给其他乘客带来不便</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/islamabad-bound-pia-flight-from-saudi-carrying-pakistan-pm-shehbaz-sharif-diverted-to-lahore-inconveniencing-other-passengers/articleshow/109201334.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109201334.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 14:29:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/islamabad-bound-pia-flight-from-saudi-carrying-pakistan-pm-shehbaz-sharif-diverted-to-lahore-inconveniencing-other-passengers/articleshow/109201334.cms</guid></item><item><title>数据显示，印度和中国是二月份俄罗斯石油的最大买家</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/business/india-china-top-buyers-of-russian-oil-in-february-data-show/articleshow/109197155.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109197155.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;据贸易商和 LSEG 数据报道，2 月份俄罗斯海运燃料油和减压柴油 (VGO) 出口继续保持主导地位，主要出口到中国和印度。自欧盟于2023年2月对俄罗斯石油产品实施全面禁运以来，这一趋势一直持续，将俄罗斯大部分燃料油和VGO转向替代市场，主要是亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 12:45:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/business/india-china-top-buyers-of-russian-oil-in-february-data-show/articleshow/109197155.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦：选举机构要求各政党在 4 月 22 日之前提交投票费用详细信息</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-electoral-body-asks-political-parties-to-submit-poll-expenses-details-by-april-22/articleshow/109197364.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109197364.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 11:51:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-electoral-body-asks-political-parties-to-submit-poll-expenses-details-by-april-22/articleshow/109197364.cms</guid></item><item><title>塔利班最高领导人罕见在开斋节公开露面：政府</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/taliban-supreme-leader-makes-rare-public-appearance-on-eid-govt/articleshow/109194748.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109194748.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;塔利班领导人罕见地公开露面，在坎大哈主持开斋节祈祷活动。保持低调并采取严格的安全措施。他的照片仅存一张。阿富汗政府发言人证实了这一事件，有数千名信徒在场。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 10:30:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/taliban-supreme-leader-makes-rare-public-appearance-on-eid-govt/articleshow/109194748.cms</guid></item><item><title>习近平：外部干涉无法阻止与台湾“家人团聚”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/external-interference-cannot-stop-family-reunion-with-taiwan-china-president-xi-jinping/articleshow/109193280.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109193280.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;​​习近平重申了海峡两岸作为中国人的共同身份，并反对外部干涉，特别是美国等西方国家的干涉，这是徒劳的。习近平在台湾媒体报道的评论中表示，“外部干涉阻挡不了国家和家庭团聚的历史潮流”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 10:01:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/external-interference-cannot-stop-family-reunion-with-taiwan-china-president-xi-jinping/articleshow/109193280.cms</guid></item><item><title>记者小组呼吁塔利班解除 Facebook 在阿富汗的禁令</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/panel-of-journalists-calls-on-taliban-to-lift-facebook-ban-in-afghanistan/articleshow/109190673.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109190673.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 08:56:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/panel-of-journalists-calls-on-taliban-to-lift-facebook-ban-in-afghanistan/articleshow/109190673.cms</guid></item><item><title>伊朗最高领袖重申承诺对以色列杀害将军进行报复</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/irans-supreme-leader-reiterates-promise-to-retaliate-against-israel-over-killings-of-generals/articleshow/109190322.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109190322.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;阿亚图拉阿里·哈梅内伊发誓要对伊朗将军在叙利亚的死亡事件进行报复，批评西方对以色列的支持，并重申伊朗的反以色列立场。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 08:51:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/irans-supreme-leader-reiterates-promise-to-retaliate-against-israel-over-killings-of-generals/articleshow/109190322.cms</guid></item><item><title>中国习近平会见台湾前领导人马英九：官方媒体</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/chinas-xi-meets-former-taiwan-leader-ma-ying-jeou-state-media/articleshow/109189717.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109189717.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;中国国家主席习近平在北京会见台湾前总统马英九，这是北京和台北领导人之间的罕见事件。马云的“和平之旅”旨在缓解双方之间的紧张关系。这次会面是继 2015 年上次会议之后的一次会面，其中包括参观科技公司和大学。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 08:32:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/chinas-xi-meets-former-taiwan-leader-ma-ying-jeou-state-media/articleshow/109189717.cms</guid></item><item><title>“与亨特·拜登有联系的乌克兰公司与俄罗斯恐怖袭击有关”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/hunter-biden-linked-ukrainian-firm-connected-to-terror-attacks-in-russia/articleshow/109184433.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109184433.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;俄罗斯调查涉及西方国家的恐怖主义融资活动，目标是在乌克兰的美国公司。与亨特·拜登有联系的布里斯马控股公司因资助恐怖行为而受到调查。美国对索赔提出争议，凸显地缘政治和商业问题，同时涉及美俄关系。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 06:04:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/hunter-biden-linked-ukrainian-firm-connected-to-terror-attacks-in-russia/articleshow/109184433.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列：停火、劫持人质、离开加沙、重新考虑一切</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/israel-cease-fire-get-hostages-leave-gaza-rethink-everything/articleshow/109184026.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109184026.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 05:51:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/israel-cease-fire-get-hostages-leave-gaza-rethink-everything/articleshow/109184026.cms</guid></item><item><title>亚洲北约：中国为何对 AUKUS 扩张持谨慎态度</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/asian-nato-why-china-is-wary-of-aukus-expansion/articleshow/109183738.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109183738.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt; AUKUS 可能扩展到日本，这引发了人们对军国主义和不稳定的担忧。美国、英国和澳大利亚讨论技术，而中国则因核扩散风险而反对。日本的国防野心也凸显出来。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 05:46:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/asian-nato-why-china-is-wary-of-aukus-expansion/articleshow/109183738.cms</guid></item><item><title>唐纳德·特朗普不再出现在彭博亿万富翁指数中</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/donald-trump-no-longer-on-bloomberg-billionaires-index/articleshow/109183522.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109183522.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;特朗普媒体的股价下跌使市值蒸发了数十亿美元，影响了特朗普的净资产和彭博排名。批评者质疑可持续性，而特朗普则为 Truth Social 辩护，表达了对其增长和未来的信心。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 05:38:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/donald-trump-no-longer-on-bloomberg-billionaires-index/articleshow/109183522.cms</guid></item><item><title>秘鲁1900年出生的124岁老人荣获世界最长寿人类称号</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/peru-claims-worlds-oldest-human-title-with-124-year-old-born-in-1900/articleshow/109181045.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109181045.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;秘鲁官员表示，安第斯山脉是长寿的关键，马塞利诺·阿巴德 (Marcelino Abad) 声称自己已经 124 岁了。凸显了阿巴德在瓦努科的健康生活方式和平和风度。秘鲁当局支持他获得吉尼斯世界纪录。阿巴德的活力秘诀包括富含水果和羊肉的饮食以及咀嚼古柯叶。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 04:20:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/peru-claims-worlds-oldest-human-title-with-124-year-old-born-in-1900/articleshow/109181045.cms</guid></item><item><title>“我们犯了无数错误”：阿里巴巴创始人马云发表长篇内部帖子走出阴影</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/we-made-countless-mistakes-alibaba-founder-jack-ma-steps-out-from-shadows-with-long-internal-post/articleshow/109181344.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109181344.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;阿里巴巴集团联合创始人马云最近从公众视野中消失，并向公司员工发出了一份重要的备忘录。马云在致辞中赞扬了首席执行官吴艾迪和董事长蔡崇信的领导能力。他指出，公司一年前决定拆分为六个部门，增强了敏捷性，更加关注客户需求，加快了决策流程。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 04:33:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/we-made-countless-mistakes-alibaba-founder-jack-ma-steps-out-from-shadows-with-long-internal-post/articleshow/109181344.cms</guid></item><item><title>韩国总统面临议会选举关键公投</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/south-koreas-president-faces-a-crucial-referendum-in-parliamentary-election/articleshow/109181022.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109181022.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;韩国总统尹锡烈周三在议会选举中面临关键的全民公投，这可能决定他是否成为跛脚鸭，或享有在其剩余三年任期内推行关键政策的授权。在选举前的几个月里，支持尹恩惠的保守派和他们的自由派竞争对手互相发表有毒言论和诽谤，这是国内分歧加深的迹象。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 04:22:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/south-koreas-president-faces-a-crucial-referendum-in-parliamentary-election/articleshow/109181022.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>